{"tid":273390,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（月經）一句到尾 自來也定係鼬","createTime":"2017-06-06T13:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T22:25:49.000Z","uid":4402,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4517b6dc2cb075855c8b239ededa52ec3329c697","tid":273390,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"自來也 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/213250_0e2e65ce682f890c171a6996a4cc5b23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F213250_0e2e65ce682f890c171a6996a4cc5b23.jpg&h=01bee005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左條村可以唔要自己條命既真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己最愛既女人唔鍾意自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己最好既朋友叛變<br />\n自己既老師比自己既好朋友殺<br />\n比自己既徒弟所殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生充滿失敗<br />\n<br />\n鼬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/213605_1732c5718247351b0ecd8518a2363232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F213605_1732c5718247351b0ecd8518a2363232.jpg&h=32930c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左條村滅自己族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扔低個細佬係條村 目的就係為左等佢變勁跟住殺自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一個完美既弟控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鼬係兩登都講到有幾咁偉大 但我個人就最鍾意自來也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd4ae1e3834daad21e1ca6793450cd6786767a5","tid":273390,"uid":37709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:46:23.000Z",